Name: xanthinuria
Definition: A purine-pyrimidine metabolic disorder characterized by deficiency of xanthine oxidase

Name: dihydropyrimidine dehydrogenase deficiency
Definition: A purine-pyrimidine metabolic disorder that is an autosomal recessive metabolic disorder in which there is absent or significantly decreased activity of dihydropyrimidine dehydrogenase

Name: Lesch-Nyhan syndrome
Definition: A germ cell cancer that has_material_basis_in cells that line the yolk sac of the embryo.
